MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2004-0041 and 2007-0475. State v. Elmore.

Licking C.P. No. 02 CR 275. On motion to consolidate direct appeal case numbers. Motion denied. On application for reopening of case No. 2004-0041. Motion denied because appellant failed to comply with the 90-day filing deadline in S.Ct.Prac.R. 11.6(A). On application for reopening of ease No. 2007-0475 under S.Ct.Prac.R. 11.6. Motion denied.

Cupp, J., not participating.
